name: Jordan 1 Retro High Rare Air Soar
description: The Air Jordan 1 Rare Air 'Soar Blue' is based on the 'Royal' colorway of the Air Jordan 1, which was Michael Jordan's personal favorite design. The shoe largely recreates the design, with Soar Blue on its tumbled leather overlays, but the toe box is finished in black leather. The collar also replaces the 'Wings' logo with 'Rare Air.'
